headline: ConocoPhillips Hits New Gas Discovery in Australia’s Otway Basin
summary: ConocoPhillips has made a promising natural gas discovery in Australia’s Otway Basin, marking the region’s first find since 2021 and raising new questions around future domestic gas supply obligations.
